    "description": "Grow your career with Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions! We are hiring a Reservation Manager for our Vijayawada team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions:\nFortune Hotels Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Fortune Hotels Ventures Solutions!",
